text: Jacek Wierzchowiecki (30 March 1944 - 1 September 2015) was a Polish equestrian. He competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Przysucha County
